casebody.data:
No. —, original.

Georgia v. Morgenthau et al. November 18, 1935. Mr. M. J. Yeomans, Attorney General of Georgia, Mr. B. D. Murphy, Assistant Attorney General, and Mr. Barry Wright for plaintiff, in support of the motion.

The motion for leave to file the bill of complaint is granted and process is ordered to issue returnable on Monday, January 20, 1936.
